age. That definitely requires some inspection!\n\n**Analyzing testing challenges**\n\nI'm thinking about the package path and whether I need to create a test in Groovy. Since only Java tests might be required, I wonder if I can invoke a static method using Java reflection. I've tried before, but maybe the class is package-private. It feels like Java might not locate the method if it's synthetic. Perhaps the Class#forName call needs to be accessed in the native-image agent run to create the necessary metadata. Let's review the user-code-filter more closely.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_0a2a56880a0f68eb016a00aba8ddec819ea4fa0de2d73f90ce\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABqAKu0OOQcfJk6prKA4lRnAjUygg3VTxmHt4E9PLXf5lQ2BS4xKuuopv5R6LTX9v-JhhNx7qZITFhNidxptJlySLtejt5j2R6B77Xd-UKEDyQfnD1q3UY1s5IT-GKmBg7cyPV-ebtKRndxSpD_5eGk4rRM9Z8-8luM5qCOjL7LhbkIMtq44zdFps2qvQumaoAxeai7cM40KW7DIV6c1EDpIZXDx9Cfyk7QYDfLanxYdN6QNe_Wgg3tCZyXRcK5TaWMn8pTYLwyljRsw70F4LMEFN5uKNgMWxlBj84A4HbPHVfZfo7QqMxP6BlX12Lthy5DCLy1pXNxZBKNbmoto00f-eidElraJkMO__Df785JDNaqVwUhba_PTNiuotrYTk5MLqKtsBzdn1whcyMInl6_KB8GEc4GrEjpXwOv8DYeoTTwQblg0HDXsnsZ1RtOvT-G8bz41U_RHEyTFWtnxxlZPrBB1ALm1WgnIdKZJq2MHHCSG2w6EKBu2tlXUe6Gv-UbN7iFOSw9mYDcD7ENO3jpSkT_1T2qznRvGyLykjNUyN9FAiyyRrteEgzHxwcW0EVp6L9T5bcZgdXXhjN0IwGlSlR9O_M4JHvXErTGm1e-pJTXvBrugFySVsOBI3pXU_H5-eHy7B_zF5Gx3rocAhvXTbHDuYQla8m7idnERFzmG8wnIF3TNE4txTpMOlHma36L2KQvYZQN7O87A1S9uS8r86of_0a7sSIRKfHmdRKuq-_WuaXM_rIIn5mGfMYNWmkCcPZD6kRjkhRJRE7MTWI-hzT-R6q1MWd7hlGDcSleNnKrgI6wSdQVY1hE2DIw-rYOp2qy7uJpa6Nxlu-c_mVtGyH4vumItSMK7hqoWFNaB6AAvpWywCoTK7Cy25-kVjBtcQEEMxi_bqRLYqZIrht7YwI-3rN3rPZw56ptg_hy2xGQL57vQnPl6MQPILfx2hqkhhFcqdPIw6MjeQokSXdUXjiWVIwsOn5oO-tHBdO_3GYc3KYG_ASjHgG4irhQ29gcDTbC8NTc3_h-LUyGUKPwI8FEaopTYnvz3WlGkFJY2ce1Fa_51DfmLZoSD_MKPZuUHHjRqj0xOc29Ey3wdC_5zn1fsAlZPZAtSkDwZb3PyXr1v2F5pIe-bpsb0Vf-YHsXUbPE2iuELzRmoBHwVWMlUr5AIp358i7ShC5lbiFLENJZknSL2zP5UTA_Drl1bX2dp99yt_erRgH5Pvg3zUgmd7dGhqP5rEZXZ9VbM_oDwgxs4vctMj7UodNNF6xFZbk5hv7p-0fuVU6X